text: Palisota preussiana is a species of plant in the Commelinaceae family. It is found in Cameroon and Equatorial Guinea. Its natural habitats are subtropical or tropical moist lowland forests and subtropical or tropical moist montane forests. It is threatened by habitat loss. ==References== ==External links== * preussiana Category:Vulnerable plants Category:Plants described in 1901 Category:Flora of Africa Category:Taxonomy articles created by Polbot
